name: Borderline Personality
description:
a very serious disturbance to one's emotions. Usually, those who experience this mental illness often feel fear of being left behind, emotionally unstable, to paranoid about themselves.

When they are anxious and depressed when their sense of belonging to their partner fades, it turns their love into a sense of wanting to control their partner's life. Therefore, also often referred to as the cause of a partner being possessive.
